name: NEFilterReport.Event
desc: A type that represents the kind of event indicated by a report.

items.name: case newFlow
items.desc: A type of event indicating the report is for a new flow.

items.name: case dataDecision
items.desc: A type of event indicating the report is about a pass/block decision made after analyzing some amount of a flow’s data.

items.name: case flowClosed
items.desc: A type of event indicating the report is for a flow’s closing.
